于哪个部门，都由此部门统一管理，其他部门不得插手。新部门所有规章制度均按照职场管理进行，如有违反，一律按照相关规定进行处罚。如果不适应新部门，可申请调离。 该网友进一步解释，事情的起因是一个00后同事工作效率比较低，别的员工8小时完成的工作他需要16个小时。上级领导质问他为什么别人可以完成，他完成不了。他顶嘴说：“那你叫别人做。”此后，公司以不符合公司要求将他辞退。这个事情最终经过劳动仲裁，判这位前员工输了仲裁。之后，公司高层便开会讨论成立了这样一个部门。 上游新闻记者随后联系到网友“奥莱斯”，该网友IP所在地显示为广东。他表示自己所在的公司成立了“新一代”部门。公司的经营范围较广，包括贸易、电商等领域，但他不方便提供公司的名字。训练服从性？年轻员工“躺平”还顶嘴，一家公司成立“专管00后部门”"},"attached_info":"ClUI1bH0qKCYg/UoEAMaCDgxODExNzczIPTDp5UGMAU4pwFAEnIJNTM3ODg0Mjc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"83 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-1328819c837c1501c31f5a84d8d8c8fb_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1655406866.59437","card_id":"Q_537785611","target":{"id":537785611,"title":"失恋分手教会了你哪些道理？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/537785611","type":"question","created":1655258274,"answer_count":41,"follower_count":112,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2506,4729,12458,2059533],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I1bH0qKCYg/UoEAMaCDgxNzg5ODE5IKL5pJUGMAA4cEATcgk1Mzc3ODU2MTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"82 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-0f2b2155ea68394f7a61f17b6ea711c8_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1655406866.5948124","card_id":"Q_537845639","target":{"id":537845639,"title":"男子称妻子「沉迷」KTV 男模，警方责令场所停业三月，这样处罚有哪些法律依据？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/537845639","type":"question","created":1655282483,"answer_count":413,"follower_count":1501,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4744,5582,10601,84437,121363],"comment_count":64,"is_following":fal